      Symbols - reusable master components

      Symbols are reusable components that you can create once and use across multiple pages or sections of your project. Whether it's a button, a header, or any other design element, you can turn it into a Symbol and place it anywhere.

      The real magic happens when you need to make changes: update the Symbol just once, and every instance of it throughout your project will automatically update.

      BYOC is Build Your Own Component

      Bridge designer-developer workflow by bringing code based components into wireframe design. BYOC helps to write custom components with HTML and CSS and incorporate it as part of your UI design. It also provides first-class support of Tailwind framework. Learn more
